Image
⦁	Make sure that at least a picture file in your folder
⦁	Insert a picture and use alt attribute when the picture doesn’t appear

#file index.html
<img src="shinchan.jpg"
    alt="This is Shinchan"
    height="200">


⦁	Turn a picture into hyperlink

#file index.html
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crayon_Shin-chan">
    <img src="shinchan.jpg"
    alt="This is Shinchan"
    height="200">
    </a>


⦁	Sometime, we need to navigate to the images folder

#file index.html
<ahref="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crayon_Shin-chan">
    <img src="/image/shinchan.jpg"
    alt="This is Shinchan"
    height="200">
</a>










